xwikidoc.title: County of Morkend
xwikidoc.content: The County of Morkend is located on the northwestern side of Kinergh between the southern end of the west spur of the (% class="twikiNewLink" %)Melthian Mountains(%%) and the (% class="twikiNewLink" %)Holbrook River(%%) . It is currently ruled by [[KondTheBerzerk>>doc:KondTheBerzerk]].
